15 puzzle for windows is powered by ruby and shoesrb 3 (GUI).

For correct puzzle work  needed:
ruby 1.9.x or older (visit http://www.ruby-lang.org/)
shoesrb 3 (visit http://shoesrb.com/) 

Example of use:
Download and install shoesrb.

 Go into All Programs, then Shoes, then Shoes. 
 A file selector box should come up. 
 Browse to your desktop and select main.rb.
 Click OK and you're on your way.
 
 OR
 
 Double click on 15Puzzle.shy file.
 
For more information please visit http://melnickforever.github.com/15Puzzle/
I hope you will enjoy this app too.

Thanks
Dmitry
